<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayā<unclear>bhyu</unclear>daya śakavaruṣa <unclear>vā</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>da 1271 virōdhi saṁvatsarada kārttika <unclear>śu</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dda 2 guruvāradaṁdu śra manumahā maṇḍaḷē
<lb n="4" break="no"/>śvaraṁ Arirāya vibhāḍa bhāṣege tappuvarā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yaragaṁḍa śrī vīra bukkaṁṇa <unclear>voḍeyara</unclear> rājyā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhyudayadali śrī maṁ<unclear>ma</unclear>hā pradhānaṁ ma<unclear>leya</unclear>
<lb n="7"/>daṁṇāyakaru cika maleya daṁṇāyakaru
<lb n="8"/><unclear>śā</unclear>leṁbaḷiya [amaḷa śrī naṁdi ?] śrī pādaṁga<unclear>ḷu</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>maṭhada śālagrāma dēvarige Amritapa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍige naḍava <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> mūḍe <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> hāne
<lb n="11"/>hadi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> varege <unclear>baṁdaṁthā</unclear> pū bāyi
<lb n="12"/>Ā pūbāyi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṁda <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> dā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>gi sarba māṁnyavāgi baṁdaṁthā pa(ṇa) <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> silā
<lb n="14"/>śāsanavāgisi<unclear>lā</unclear> pritiṣṭeyanu māḍiko
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṭṭe <unclear>U</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

<p>Rest is badly worn out.</p>

<!--<h4>Top of the slab.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="16"/>kālē kālē pālaniyō bhavadbhiḥ sarvānēvaṁ bā
</p>

<!--<h4>Left side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="17" break="no"/>vinaḥ pārthivēṁdrān bhūyō bhūyō yācatē rāmacaṁdraḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

